      "value": "John Robson's 1842 scholarly collection edits three independent anonymous Middle English verse romances from a principal Taylor MS. 9 text, supplemented in selected passages through Madden's and Weber's earlier printed editions. CME00113 encodes the reprint title matter and the three poem texts, not the full editorial volume.",
